%% Shopify Support Automation — Request Sequence
%% Export: mmdc -i docs/sequence_diagram.mmd -o docs/sequence_diagram.png -b transparent

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Customer
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>POST /support
    participant Runner as ADK Runner
    participant Root as SupportRootAgent
    participant Intent as Intent Agent
    participant Priority as Priority Agent
    participant Reply as Reply Agent
    participant Escalation as Escalation Agent
    participant State as Session State
    participant Agg as build_final_response()

    Customer->>API: SupportRequest { message }
    API->>Runner: run_async(user_message)
    Runner->>Root: invoke orchestrator

    Root->>Intent: run_async(ctx)
    Intent->>Intent: Gemini classify intent
    Intent->>State: write intent_result
    Intent-->>Root: event

    Root->>Priority: run_async(ctx)
    Priority->>State: read intent_result
    Priority->>Priority: Gemini assign priority
    Priority->>State: write priority_result
    Priority-->>Root: event

    Root->>Reply: run_async(ctx)
    Reply->>State: read intent_result, priority_result
    Reply->>Reply: Gemini generate reply
    Reply->>State: write reply_result
    Reply-->>Root: event

    Root->>Escalation: run_async(ctx)
    Escalation->>State: read intent, priority, reply
    Escalation->>Escalation: Gemini decide escalate
    Escalation->>State: write escalation_result
    Escalation-->>Root: event

    Root->>Agg: build_final_response(state)
    Agg->>State: read all specialist keys
    Agg-->>Root: SupportResponse
    Root->>State: write final_response
    Root-->>Runner: final event (JSON)
    Runner-->>API: SupportResponse
    API-->>Customer: 200 OK { intent, priority, reply, escalate }
